high_descs: Turn around and go to the stove.
Pick up the knife next to the sponge.
Turn right and go to the counter on the right of the stove.
Cut the tomato on the counter behind the knife.
Turn around, go across the room, turn right and go to the microwave.
Put the knife on the left side of the microwave.
Turn right and go back to the counter with the sliced tomato.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the counter.
Turn around and head to the sink.
Put the slice of tomato in the sink, rinse it and pick it back up.
Turn around and go to the microwave.
Put the slice of tomato on the left side of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean slice of tomato next to the microwave.

Set the knife down to the left of the microwave on the stand.
Go to the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn and go to the sink.
Wash the tomato slice in the sink.
Turn and walk back to the microwave stand.
Set the clean tomato slice on the stand.
